♪ Yeah ♪

35:38.485 --> 35:39.862
♪ Yeah ♪

35:39.864 --> 35:41.715
♪ The sidewalk told me the path taken ♪

35:41.717 --> 35:43.343
♪ And he said the road less traveled ♪

35:43.345 --> 35:44.521
♪ Is for the humble and patient ♪

35:44.523 --> 35:47.420
♪ He said the road carries
risk and many broken bridges ♪

